<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Seiczen
                            <expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>leins</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz der
                        schof bey uns gekawfft <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süll und begert, daz
                        wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darumb czerede
                            <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Nu <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache nichts, so habt ir uns auch keinen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief benant
                        und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> nicht, ob ir einen
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mer <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> maint. Dann weliche
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        mainten, den <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> sie
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ir <expan>scheinbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte bey uns mit
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol czüsprechen. Was
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> rechtes <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> tün
                                <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dary<ex>n</ex>nen</expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> sein. Und das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> uns
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief braht hat, auch also gesagt.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                        Cecilie.</ab>
